data.description: FULLY UPDATED....NO REAR NEIGHBORS  Welcome to this inviting 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home located in the charming community of Spring Hill. This residence offers a warm and spacious interior, perfect for family living. The well-appointed kitchen, comfortable living spaces, and abundant natural light make this home both functional and inviting. The backyard provides a lovely outdoor space for relaxation and gatherings. Conveniently situated near schools, parks, and amenities, this property is a wonderful opportunity for those seeking a comfortable family home in a highly sought after community. Don't miss your chance to make 3798 Braemere Dr your new address.
